# ResQ Plate — UI Uplift & Phase 2 Implementation Plan

## Overview

This plan covers two distinct workstreams:

1. **UI/UX Uplift (Frontend)** — A cinematic public landing page, and significant dashboard improvements for both Donors and Recipients.
2. **Phase 2: AI Agent Expansion (MCP Integration)** — Introducing a Spring AI MCP server that exposes platform operations as AI-callable tools.

---

## Part 1: UI/UX Uplift

### New Routes

The current app sends `/` directly to `/auth`. We'll add a public landing page at `/`.

```
/              → LandingPage.jsx  (NEW — public)
/auth          → AuthPage.jsx     (IMPROVE)
/donor         → DonorDashboard.jsx (IMPROVE)
