### MCP Server Registration

#### [NEW] `src/main/java/com/resq/ResQ_Plate/config/McpServerConfig.java`

```java
@Configuration
public class McpServerConfig {
    @Bean
    public ToolCallbackProvider resqTools(
        AdminCopilotTools adminTools,
        NgoClaimAgentTools claimTools,
        SupportBotTools supportTools
    ) {
        return MethodInvokingToolCallbackProvider.builder()
            .toolObjects(adminTools, claimTools, supportTools)
            .build();
    }
}
```

